  <ul>
    <li>Necrophilia</li>
    <li>Scat</li>
    <li>Beastiality (shifters accepted in human form)</li>
    <li>Incest (not even the illusion of it)</li>
    <li>Rape for titillation</li>
    <li>Racist Rhetoric</li>
    <li>Pedophilia</li>
    <li>Sex between under age children</li>
    <li>Copyrighted material (such as lyrics)</li>
    <li>Plagirism</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

    <h2>Guidelines</h2>
    <p>Complete manuscript in WORD formatted to the below specifications:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>1-inch margins</li>
      <li>12 pt. Times New Roman Font</li>
      <li>Headers/Footers/Page Numbers</li>
      <li>Double Spaced</li>
      <li>1 page synopsis</li>
      <li>Your submission should be fully edited before submitting</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Please send submissions by email to submissions@ownvoicespublishing.com with the following information:
      Query letter with legal name, pen name (if applicable), working title, word count, genre, and a 1 page synopsis attached,
      along with any previous writing credits.</p>
    <p>Please allow 8-12 weeks for response.</p>
    <p>These guidelines subject to change.</p>
